HEADWORD: Stocah
<hw>Sto"cah</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Ir. & Gael.
<ets>stocach</ets> an idle fellow who lives on the industry of others, a
lounger.]</ety> <def>A menial attendant.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
